Melana is a dynamic custom voiced follower which progresses while adventuring with the player.

Voiced by the very talented KiaraRedVA who also wrote half of the voice lines.

Rescue a young timid maid and watch her slowly become a fierce warrior.

Dear Bethesda,



Your civil war sucks. Someone else fixed it for you.

I've kept a focus on keeping it as close to vanilla as possible and to not stray too far from the personalities given.

State.Author: Lollia aka SkyrimSplicer
State.Description: Uses carefully spliced and re-purposed dialogue to allow the citizens of Morthal to interact with each another. Along with giving more immersive schedules to the inhabitants, it also expands the skills and backstories of Benor, Eisa Blackthorn, Valdimar and Erandur.

Enjoy!

State.Description:
Adds several dialogue options to most of Skyrim's NPCs (even ones initially without any dialogue options) allowing for increased immersive interactions and role-play. 



Compatible with every dialogue overhaul / commentary mod such as FCO SE, RDO, GDO and others as it does not conflict or replace and only adds more dialogue.

State.Description:
A very simple and compatible version of Immersive Spell Learning, using Don't Eat Spell Tomes, with added features from another bunch of similar mods.

 Survival Mode and SunHelm compatible.

State.Description:
NPCs with more extensive dialogue and role play choices. Over 250+ fully voiced NPCs, 25+ followers, 15+ marriage NPCs, and 50+ quests.
